      <Card imgSrc="/public/assets/how/4.png" title="Discover the Deals" description="Obtain special offers from our expert agents that will contact you to tailor your needs." />
      <Card imgSrc="/public/assets/how/5.png" title="Grab your Offer" description="Choose the best deal for you and lock down the best opportunity for your next casino visit." />
